obj_root_law_sections_37_content:
  string
  line `The Assam Sales of Motor Spirit`
  line `and Lubricants Taxation Act, 1939, as extended to Manipur shall stand repealed:`
  line
  line `Provided that such repeal shall not affect--`
  line
  line `(a) the previous operation of the said Act or anything duly done or suffered thereunder; or`
  line
  line `(b) any right, privilege, obligation or liability acquired, accrued or incurred under the said Act; or`
  line
  line `(c) any penalty, forfeiture or punishment incurred in respect of any offence committed against the`
  line `said Act; or`
  line
  line `(d) any investigation, legal proceeding or remedy in respect of any such right, privilege,`
  line `obligation, liability, penalty, forfeiture or punishment as aforesaid:`
  line
  line `Provided further that anything done or any action taken (including any appointment or delegation`
  line `made, notification, instruction or direction issued, certificate of registration granted) under the Act hereby`
  line `repealed shall be deemed to have been done or taken under the corresponding provision of this Act and`
  line `shall continue to be in force accordingly unless and until superseded by anything done or any action taken`
  line `under this Act.`
obj_root_law_sections_37_footnotes:
  string
  line
